<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木偶师傅为了成功地偷走匹诺曹，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快地收拾好自己的马车，准备离开小镇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他着急离开，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他把他的钱袋子、工具和帐篷都堆到了关匹诺曹的笼子上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>随着马车移动，最重的袋子掉到了匹诺曹的身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在匹诺曹已经不哭了，但他还是很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他能感觉到马车的颠簸和晃动，但是他只能看到麻袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，这些袋子里面装的是什么呢？”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里面一定有什么东西可以帮助我逃跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手臂尽量地伸出笼子，然后悄悄地打开了第一个袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手伸进袋子里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “哦！这个袋子里面装的都是硬币呀！最少也有一百里拉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把一些硬币抓到笼子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>令他惊讶的是，那并不是硬币——而是纯金！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要发财啦！现在，我可以给杰佩托买一件大衣了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是这些硬币不会帮我逃脱这个笼子。我必须继续寻找。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他小心地悄悄地行动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手伸进了第二个袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。这个袋子里面有很多不同的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不知道都有什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让我把它们一个一个都拿出来看看吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 一个哨子？不，这个没有用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 一个汤匙？不，这个没有用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 一本书？不，这个也没有用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 一些火柴？嗯。我有办法啦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹等着马车停下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他拿起书，把它包在他的腿上，并点燃了书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他把火柴扔进了马车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “救命！”他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“着火了！我着火了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木偶师傅听到了匹诺曹的呼救声，也闻到了烧焦的味道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑到马车的后面，快速地卸下行李。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他试图找到火源。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他到达匹诺曹的笼子时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓住笼子，并打开了笼子上面的锁，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把匹诺曹从里面拉了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他找了一块毯子盖在了匹诺曹的腿上，想要将火扑灭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，那边还在烧着！”匹诺曹指了指马车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不好了！我的帐篷着火了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人大叫着，赶着去把火扑灭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在木偶师傅试图挽救他的帐篷时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹悄悄从毯子里爬出来，跑进了附近的树林里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当大火被扑灭时，匹诺曹早已不见踪影。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他依然可以听到那个人在远处大喊大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！等一下！匹诺曹，快回来！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会让你成为明星的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹跑啊跑啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但无论多努力地跑，他都没有跑到一个熟悉的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹停了下来，坐在了一个树桩上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我迷路了！”他喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找不到村子，我不知道该怎么办。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人来救我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹不知道的是，森林中有许多动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些诚实善良，但有些却贪婪无比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>